snippet.title: Post-Shift - Teaser Trailer (FNaF Fangame)
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! I thought I'd make a quick teaser trailer showing the characters and some gameplay! I'm hoping I can get this game done relatively soon, however, I can't pinpoint an exact date yet unfortunately (I'm hoping late this month or April).

Enjoy this quick teaser trailer though! :)

Sorry for the lack of trailer text as well, I wanted to show mainly gameplay and the characters for this.

Check out the gamejolt page here! https://gamejolt.com/games/post-shift/169078
